title: Bug 121687: Exception thrown when exporting data in a table inside a grid cell.
OB: Exception is thrown when trying to export data in a table that is inside a grid cell.
EB: When exporting data in two tables, the expected result is that the data is exported successfully. However, the actual result is an exception being thrown in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() method.
SR: To reproduce the bug, follow these steps: 1. Insert one table into a grid cell. 2. Insert another table into the other grid cell. 3. Export the data from the tables.
